text: Ngazibini Sigwili (born 12 June 1995) is a South African cricketer. He was part of South Africa's squad for the 2014 ICC Under-19 Cricket World Cup. He was included in the Eastern Province cricket team squad for the 2015 Africa T20 Cup.Eastern Province Squad / Players – ESPNcricinfo.
